      <h1 class="display-1">Mortgage Broker vs Loan Officer: What's the Difference?</h1>
      <p class="lead hero-subtitle">Same license, different path. A loan officer originates loans; a mortgage broker does it independently across many lenders. Here's the real difference &mdash; and how to choose which one fits you.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#compare" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">See the Comparison</a>
        <a href="#choose" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Which Fits You?</a>
